  <description>
    <p>
        The goal of the solution is to create a financial accounting application that is intuitive, efficient, and inclusive. 
        That empowers users to effortlessly manage their finances while ensuring that no one is left behind.
    </p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Accounting</li>
        <li>Budget Categories</li>
        <li>Bills, Transfers, Incomes (Invoices)</li>
        <li>Goals Definition</li>
        <li>Exchange rates</li>
        <li>Metrics</li>
        <li>Synchronization between devices (P2P) </li>
        <li>Recovery via WebDav or a direct File</li>
        <li>Import from CSV, QIF, OFX files for Bills and Invoices</li>
        <li>Data encryption</li>
        <li>Localization: EN, BE, PL, PT, FR, DE, UK</li>
        <li>Responsive and Adaptive Design</li>
        <li>Shortcuts</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        This is the "open-source code" application that welcomes and values contributions from the community. 
        However, there are some limitations when it comes to making external modifications and distributions, 
        as it follows the CC-BY-NC-ND-4.0 license. As the project's author, I am committed to upholding the 
        "Terms of Use" and "Privacy Policy" to ensure the well-being and satisfaction of all users across 
        all platforms (desktop, mobile, and web).
    </p>
  </description>
